title: Heig`s Base for 1.6.1170.0
description: A small modpack based on Skyrim Essentials and tech. parts of Ro and Do Not Go Gently - there is no mods that changing gameplay, crafting, perks of anything like that. Just frameworks like OAR, FLM, KID, SPID, and fixes like USSEP, USMP, script and mesh fixes. Also - AIT for UI; Dual Wield Parry - and they are disableable if you want. Everything just for start creating your own modpack!
author: Heig
